review_text: Excellent park for all ages, Big enough playground for kids, spaces for picnics, and not many people in place. Only tjing is that there are not many trees so the sun is strong.
Good park. Some pieces were broken or close to breaking. My 5 yr old had a blast.

(Translated by Google) I love this park. It is designed for children of all ages. From 2 to 11. Convenient and interesting.
